Class Parameter

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.r2dbc.core.Parameter
@Deprecated(since="6.0") public final class Parameter extends Object
Deprecated.
since 6.0, use io.r2dbc.spi.Parameter instead.
A database value that can be set in a statement.
